    {
      "text": "Hi, I'm Sanja Vinagam, a biotechnology",
      "start": 0.4,
      "duration": 5.84
    },
    {
      "text": "student passionate about using nature's",
      "start": 3.76,
      "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
      "text": "own mechanisms to solve some of our",
      "start": 6.24,
      "duration": 5.439
    },
    {
      "text": "greatest environmental challenges. Today",
      "start": 8.48,
      "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
      "text": "we are going to explore the science",
      "start": 11.679,
      "duration": 4.241
    },
    {
      "text": "behind bioluminescent trees, an idea",
      "start": 13.2,
      "duration": 7.04
    },
    {
      "text": "that would revolutionize urban lighting.",
      "start": 15.92,
      "duration": 6.24
    },
    {
      "text": "Did you know street lighting actually",
      "start": 20.24,
      "duration": 4.56
    },
    {
      "text": "consumes around 19% of global",
      "start": 22.16,
      "duration": 5.52
    },
    {
      "text": "electricity, contributing heavily to",
      "start": 24.8,
      "duration": 6.08
    },
    {
      "text": "energy cost and CO2 emissions?",
      "start": 27.68,
      "duration": 6.08
    },
    {
      "text": "Now, what if we could reduce this by",
      "start": 30.88,
      "duration": 5.6
    },
    {
      "text": "harnessing nature's ability to produce",
      "start": 33.76,
      "duration": 4.06
    },
    {
      "text": "light?",
      "start": 36.48,
      "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
      "text": "[Music]",
      "start": 37.82,
      "duration": 3.86
    },
    {
      "text": "Bioluminescent is a natural phenomenon",
      "start": 39.12,
      "duration": 6.64
    },
    {
      "text": "in which living organisms produce light.",
      "start": 41.68,
      "duration": 6.08
    },
    {
      "text": "This occurs in species such as",
      "start": 45.76,
      "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
      "text": "jellyfish, fireflies, and even certain",
      "start": 47.76,
      "duration": 4.479
    },
    {
      "text": "algae.",
      "start": 50.48,
      "duration": 4.239
    },
    {
      "text": "This process is driven by a biochemical",
      "start": 52.239,
      "duration": 5.361
    },
    {
      "text": "reaction involving a molecule called",
      "start": 54.719,
      "duration": 5.121
    },
    {
      "text": "luciferin and an enzyme called",
      "start": 57.6,
      "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
      "text": "luciferase.",
      "start": 59.84,
      "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
      "text": "When luciferin is oxidized by",
      "start": 61.76,
      "duration": 4.96
    },
    {
      "text": "luciferase, it releases photons",
      "start": 63.76,
      "duration": 7.32
    },
    {
      "text": "resulting in a natural glow.",
      "start": 66.72,
      "duration": 4.36
    },
    {
      "text": "[Music]",
      "start": 72.07,
      "duration": 6.98
    },
    {
      "text": "Scientists are now working to",
      "start": 79.119,
      "duration": 4.401
    },
    {
      "text": "incorporate this bioluminescent genes",
      "start": 80.88,
      "duration": 5.44
    },
    {
      "text": "into plants, allowing trees to emit",
      "start": 83.52,
      "duration": 6.32
    },
    {
      "text": "light just as these organisms do. This",
      "start": 86.32,
      "duration": 4.96
    },
    {
      "text": "could eliminate the need for",
      "start": 89.84,
      "duration": 5.12
    },
    {
      "text": "conventional street lights.",
      "start": 91.28,
      "duration": 5.76
    },
    {
      "text": "Recent advancements in genetic",
      "start": 94.96,
      "duration": 4.32
    },
    {
      "text": "engineering have allowed researchers to",
      "start": 97.04,
      "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
      "text": "insert bioluminescent genes from",
      "start": 99.28,
      "duration": 5.36
    },
    {
      "text": "organisms like fireflies and bacteria",
      "start": 101.68,
      "duration": 5.92
    },
    {
      "text": "into plant DNA. A study published in",
      "start": 104.64,
      "duration": 5.68
    },
    {
      "text": "Nature Biotechnology demonstrated the",
      "start": 107.6,
      "duration": 5.28
    },
    {
      "text": "successful creation of glowing tobacco",
      "start": 110.32,
      "duration": 6.4
    },
    {
      "text": "plants using luciferase from fireflies.",
      "start": 112.88,
      "duration": 6.0
    },
    {
      "text": "Researchers have now moved beyond",
      "start": 116.72,
      "duration": 4.8
    },
    {
      "text": "initial experiments with small plants",
      "start": 118.88,
      "duration": 5.12
    },
    {
      "text": "and are working on engineering larger",
      "start": 121.52,
      "duration": 4.8
    },
    {
      "text": "trees that could serve as urban street",
      "start": 124.0,
      "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
      "text": "lights.",
      "start": 126.32,
      "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
      "text": "These trees could be designed to glow",
      "start": 128.64,
      "duration": 4.56
    },
    {
      "text": "more intensely in the dark and dimmer",
      "start": 130.72,
      "duration": 4.8
    },
    {
      "text": "when exposed to daylight, reducing",
      "start": 133.2,
      "duration": 7.119
    },
    {
      "text": "energy consumption and light pollution.",
      "start": 135.52,
      "duration": 6.719
    },
    {
      "text": "The environmental implications of",
      "start": 140.319,
      "duration": 5.121
    },
    {
      "text": "bioluminescent trees are profound.",
      "start": 142.239,
      "duration": 5.121
    },
    {
      "text": "According to a study published in",
      "start": 145.44,
      "duration": 5.04
    },
    {
      "text": "Science Advances, urban areas using",
      "start": 147.36,
      "duration": 5.76
    },
    {
      "text": "bioluminescent trees for lighting could",
      "start": 150.48,
      "duration": 5.68
    },
    {
      "text": "reduce carbon emissions by 30%, making",
      "start": 153.12,
      "duration": 5.36
    },
    {
      "text": "cities significantly more sustainable",
      "start": 156.16,
      "duration": 5.92
    },
    {
      "text": "and also saving the earth. Furthermore,",
      "start": 158.48,
      "duration": 5.759
    },
    {
      "text": "because these trees would be powered by",
      "start": 162.08,
      "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
      "text": "their own metabolic processes,",
      "start": 164.239,
      "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
      "text": "maintenance and energy costs would be",
      "start": 166.72,
      "duration": 5.12
    },
    {
      "text": "drastically lower. It's not just about",
      "start": 168.959,
      "duration": 5.601
    },
    {
      "text": "replacing lights. This is about creating",
      "start": 171.84,
      "duration": 5.119
    },
    {
      "text": "living infrastructure that works in",
      "start": 174.56,
      "duration": 6.399
    },
    {
      "text": "harmony with nature.",
      "start": 176.959,
      "duration": 6.801
    },
    {
      "text": "Bioluminescent trees represent a new",
      "start": 180.959,
      "duration": 6.801
    },
    {
      "text": "frontier in sustainable urban planning.",
      "start": 183.76,
      "duration": 7.04
    },
    {
      "text": "By merging biotechnology with ecology,",
      "start": 187.76,
      "duration": 5.36
    },
    {
      "text": "we could light up our cities while",
      "start": 190.8,
      "duration": 5.519
    },
    {
      "text": "reducing our carbon footprint.",
      "start": 193.12,
      "duration": 6.08
    },
    {
      "text": "Now, this isn't just a distant dream.",
      "start": 196.319,
      "duration": 4.961
    },
    {
      "text": "It's a glimpse into a greener and",
      "start": 199.2,
